name: My Indecisiveness Earrings
description: Indecisive? Me too! Give a little glam to your indecisiveness with these absolutely gorgeous earrings. One earring is made of a brass coin with the word "non" on it. The other earring is made of the same brass coin, but this time the word "oui" is present. At the top of each coin is a vintage coral lily (made of plastic). Earrings are finished with 14K gold-filled earring hooks. They measure 1.75 inches from top of hook to bottom of earring.

name: Kiss Me, You Fool - Earrings
description: These incredibly lightweight earrings are adorable, fun and add a little something to just about any outfit. Brass boy and girl kissing charms dangle from each earring. One side has a round "LOVE" charm and the other side has a matching round charm, this time with the word "AMOUR". Each are raw brass. Peach colored roses add color to the whole ensemble. Earrings are finished with gold-filled earring hooks. The longer earring measure 4 inches from the very top of the earring hook to the bottom of the earring. The shorter earring measures 3.5 inches.

name: I Left My Heart In Paris - Earrings
description:
Whether you've been there and want to go back or it's just always been a dream that you've had, these earrings bring along the perfect sentiment. A brass round charm with the word "LOVE" on it is adorned with a brass Eiffel Tower charm. A cream colored rose made of vintage plastic tops off the design. These dangle from brass vintaged earring hooks.

Earrings measure about 1.25 inches from the bottom of the earring hook to the bottom of the "love" charm. They are about 0.75 inches wide.

name: Elegance - Pink and Ivory Earrings
description: Pink Mother of Pearl "donuts" sit behind ivory colored vintage plastic roses to create these earrings. The color combination and overall appearance make these earrings elegant, feminine and cute all in one. The dangle from 14K gold-filled earring hooks. Earrings measure 2 inches from the top of the earring hooks to the bottom of the pink "donuts".

name: Love To Love Ya Baby - Earrings
description: What a great statement these feminine earrings make! A single raw brass circular charm about 3/4 of an inch simply states "LOVE". A coral colored plastic lily adds a little more charm to these already charming earrings. They dangle from gold-filled earring hooks. From top of earring hooks, earrings measure about 1-3/4 inches long.
